Restriction for Data
====================
All datasets, raw signals, processed data, train schedules, and any derived
information (collectively referred to as "Data") included in this repository
are confidential and subject to the following terms:

1. The Data is provided exclusively for internal use by the SMART-BRIDGES-ES
   consortium and authorized collaborators.
2. The Data may not be copied, redistributed, published, sold, or used for
   any purpose outside the scope of the project without explicit written
   authorization from the consortium.
3. Any unauthorized disclosure or distribution of the Data is strictly prohibited
   and may be subject to legal action.

For questions or permissions regarding the Data, please contact the project coordinators.